.88,"line":54}],"lines":[{"s":6.74,"e":7.46,"text":"♪♪"},{"s":8.16,"e":12.14,"text":"♪ Mm-mm-mm-mm ♪"},{"s":15.5,"e":16.22,"text":"♪♪"},{"s":16.22,"e":21.2,"text":"♪ Under the stars, I took the long way down ♪"},{"s":21.2,"e":24.78,"text":"♪ Past St. John's soup kitchen, past the shuttered town ♪"},{"s":24.78,"e":28.48,"text":"♪ Steam from the bowl, salt in the cold air ♪"},{"s":28.48,"e":32.08,"text":"♪ Hands at the door like a prayer laid bare ♪"},{"s":32.08,"e":34.16,"text":"♪ FBI van parked by the curbside edge ♪"},{"s":34.16,"e":35.7,"text":"♪ Juggalos laugh on the chain-link ledge ♪"},{"s":35.7,"e":37.48,"text":"♪ Time travelers blink, then they vanish clean ♪"},{"s":37.48,"e":39.32,"text":"♪ Like a bad dream folding in the scene ♪"},{"s":39.32,"e":41.1,"text":"♪ Ain't your hands draw signs and the dust on stone? ♪"},{"s":41.1,"e":42.88,"text":"♪ Multi-sentient voices in one throat tone ♪"},{"s":42.88,"e":46.66,"text":"♪ Aliens lean in with a silver grin, say, you've been lost but you still fit in ♪"},{"s":46.66,"e":50.2,"text":"♪ Angels above me, demons below ♪"},{"s":50.2,"e":53.62,"text":"♪ Djinn in the hallway, tell me what I know ♪"},{"s":53.62,"e":57.2,"text":"♪ Souls in the rafters, ghosts in the rain ♪"},{"s":57.2,"e":61.38,"text":"♪ All of them call me back to my name ♪"},{"s":61.58,"e":69.84,"text":"♪ Under the stars, tattooed on my scars ♪"},{"s":69.84,"e":78.86,"text":"♪ Heaven and hell, sleep in the mines ♪"},{"s":78.86,"e":82.34,"text":"♪ Sleep in the mines ♪"},{"s":82.34,"e":84.04,"text":"♪ At the soup line, everybody got a cold ♪"},{"s":84.04,"e":85.74,"text":"♪ Bread in a bowl and a map to the road ♪"},{"s":85.74,"e":87.54,"text":"♪ A cop and a tie and a clown with a crown ♪"},{"s":87.54,"e":89.12,"text":"♪ Both keep staring like they know this town ♪"},{"s":89.12,"e":90.9,"text":"♪ An alien child with a paper plate ♪"},{"s":90.9,"e":92.58,"text":"♪ Asks if the end is just a change of state ♪"},{"s":92.58,"e":93.96,"text":"♪ I said, maybe if the moon says so ♪"},{"s":93.96,"e":96.18,"text":"♪ Then the walls lit up with a soft white glow ♪"},{"s":96.18,"e":99.8,"text":"♪ Ghost in the corner, she tapped my sleeve, said, don't trust the ones who promise leave ♪"},{"s":99.8,"e":104.26,"text":"♪ Smile with a borrowed face, an angel cried in a flawless place ♪"},{"s":104.26,"e":107.6,"text":"♪ Angels above me, demons below ♪"},{"s":107.6,"e":111.04,"text":"♪ Djinn in the hallway, tell me what I know ♪"},{"s":111.04,"e":114.56,"text":"♪ Souls in the rafters, ghosts in the rain ♪"},{"s":114.56,"e":118.74,"text":"♪ All of them call me back to my name ♪"},{"s":119.08,"e":126.44,"text":"♪ Under the stars, tattooed on my scars ♪"},{"s":126.44,"e":133.56,"text":"♪ Heaven and hell, sleeping in my arms ♪"},{"s":136.4,"e":141.64,"text":"♪ Sleeping in my arms ♪"},{"s":144.58,"e":150.18,"text":"♪ I seen the old rice in the basement ring ♪"},{"s":150.18,"e":153.72,"text":"♪ Saw twelve moons rise from a paper king ♪"},{"s":153.72,"e":157.3,"text":"♪ Saw one face split into three, then four ♪"},{"s":157.3,"e":160.76,"text":"♪ Then the room went still like an open door ♪"},{"s":160.76,"e":164.02,"text":"♪ If you're a sinner, if you made a light ♪"},{"s":164.02,"e":167.38,"text":"♪ If you came from ash, or you came from night ♪"},{"s":167.38,"e":170.76,"text":"♪ If you're here to stay, or just passing through ♪"},{"s":170.76,"e":176.72,"text":"♪ The sky keeps room for the strange and true ♪"},{"s":176.72,"e":181.44,"text":"♪ All of them, all of them, under the stars ♪"},{"s":181.44,"e":184.98,"text":"♪ All of them, all of them, tattooed on my scars ♪"},{"s":184.98,"e":188.66,"text":"♪ All of them, all of them, heaven and hell ♪"},{"s":188.66,"e":191.68,"text":"♪ All of them, all of them, sleeping in my arms ♪"},{"s":191.68,"e":195.36,"text":"♪ Souls and ghosts and names unseen ♪"},{"s":195.36,"e":198.98,"text":"♪ All that falls between the beams ♪"},{"s":198.98,"e":206.08,"text":"♪ Under the stars, I still believe there's room for you and room for me ♪"},{"s":206.72,"e":210.12,"text":"♪ Hoo-hoo, hoo-hoo, hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo ♪"},{"s":210.12,"e":219.88,"text":"♪ Hoo-hoo, hoo-hoo, hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo"}],"duration":222.72000122070312,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:26:07.642Z","model":"whisper-1"}